texts: This is Bob's plan for April 01 2023: Wake up and have breakfast with family at 7:00 am,Drop daughter off at school at 8:00 am,Head to the mechanic shop and work on a car from 9:00 am to 12:00 pm,Take a lunch break and have a barbecue rib sandwich at a nearby restaurant at 12:30 pm,Return to the shop and work on another car from 1:30 pm to 4:00 pm,Attend a football game with friends at 7:00 pm,Head back home and spend quality time with family before going to bed at 10:00 pm.
